each of the hall treatments to
talk the matter over with individual hall members. He indicated that he favors the idea of
all calls keeping their TV'ii
Within the men’s residence hall
system, and all but one at the
North treatments backed him
with a resolution of similar
opinion.
Most calls don't want to commit themselves definitely—it's
easier to wait and See what
everybody else does — but a
sensitive headcount shows six
calls (Smith, Cowles, Gates,
East and West morris, and
Langan) in favor of remaining
their tubes, one hall (Clark) in
gambling or selling theory, and
four calls (watson, liable, and
North and South counties) still
undefined.
